---

<Layout 
  title="ចុងភៅ ចេង គួងម៉េង - CKM Catering Service | 金边顶级外烩服务" 
  description="CKM Catering 提供金边最顶级的婚宴外烩、商务聚餐与私人厨师服务。提供正宗高棉菜与中式宴席，品质保证。សេវាកម្មម្ហូបការ និងកម្មវិធីជប់លៀងដ៏ល្អឥតខ្ចោះ។"
  image={heroImage}
>
  
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 bg-dark/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/10 shadow-lg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src={logo} alt="CKM Logo" class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full border-2 border-gold shadow-glow">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl font-heading tracking-wider">CKM CATERING</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Cheng Koung Meng</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
           <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-[#2AABEE] transition">
             <i class="fab fa-telegram"></i> Telegram
           </a>
           <a href="#contact" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primaryLight text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm transition shadow-lg hover:scale-105 flex flex-col items-center leading-none">
             <span>Contact Us</span>
             <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-chinese opacity-90 mt-0.5">联系我们</span>
           </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-fixed transform scale-105" style={`background-image: url('${heroImage}');`}></div>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/60 to-dark"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up">
        <img src={logo} alt="CKM Logo" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full border-4 border-gold mx-auto mb-8 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(212,175,55,0.6)] animate-pulse-slow">
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-heading leading-tight drop-shadow-2xl">
          ចុងភៅ <span class="text-gold">ចេង គួងម៉េង</span>
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-chinese tracking-wide">
          金边<span class="text-gold">顶级</span>宴会餐饮服务
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 mb-2 font-light">
          សេវាកម្មម្ហូបការ និងកម្មវិធីជប់លៀងដ៏ល្អឥតខ្ចោះនៅភ្នំពេញ
        </p>
        <p class="text-gold text-sm mb-10 tracking-widest uppercase">
          Premium Wedding & Event Catering Service
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" class="bg-[#2AABEE] hover:bg-[#1e95d4] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(42,171,238,0.4)] flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i class="fab fa-telegram-plane text-xl"></i> 
                <div class="flex flex-col items-start leading-none">
                    <span>Telegram</span>
                    <span class="text-[0.65rem] font-chinese">线上咨询</span>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+85512977696" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-dark text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-start leading-none">
                    <span>Call Now</span>
                    <span class="text-[0.65rem] font-chinese">立即致电</span>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce text-white/50">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-2xl"></i>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="py-20 bg-dark relative">
     <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
     <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white font-heading mb-2">ហេតុអ្វីជ្រើសរើស <span class="text-gold">CKM?</span></h2>
            <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-400 font-chinese mb-4">为什么选择我们?</h3>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
                <i class="fas fa-gem text-4xl text-gold mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-heading">គុណភាពល្អឯក</h3>
                <h4 class="text-lg text-gold font-chinese mb-3 font-bold">顶级品质</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-2">យើងខ្ញុំជ្រើសរើសតែគ្រឿងផ្សំស្រស់ៗ និងល្អបំផុត។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-chinese">严选最新鲜、最优质的食材，确保每一道菜肴的完美口感。</p>
             </div>
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
                <i class="fas fa-star text-4xl text-gold mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-heading">បទពិសោធន៍</h3>
                <h4 class="text-lg text-gold font-chinese mb-3 font-bold">经验丰富</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-2">បទពិសោធន៍ជាច្រើនឆ្នាំក្នុងការរៀបចំកម្មវិធីមង្គលការ។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-chinese">拥有多年承办大型婚宴与高端商务宴请的丰富经验。</p>
             </div>
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
                <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell text-4xl text-gold mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-heading">សេវាកម្ម</h3>
                <h4 class="text-lg text-gold font-chinese mb-3 font-bold">至尊服务</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-2">ក្រុមការងារជំនាញរបស់យើងនឹងផ្តល់ជូននូវបទពិសោធន៍ដ៏រលូន។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm font-chinese">专业团队为您提供无微不至的一站式宴会服务體驗。</p>
             </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-cream text-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-2 font-heading text-dark">ដំណើរការសេវាកម្ម</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 font-chinese mb-16 text-xl">服务流程</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[16%] right-[16%] h-1 bg-gray-200 -z-10"></div>
            
            {[
                {icon: "fa-comments", step: "1", title: "ការប្រឹក្សាយោបល់", cnTitle: "需求咨询", desc: "ពិភាក្សាអំពីតម្រូវការ និងថវិការបស់អ្នក"},
                {icon: "fa-utensils", step: "2", title: "រៀបចំបញ្ជីមុខម្ហូប", cnTitle: "定制菜单", desc: "ជ្រើសរើសមុខម្ហូបពិសេសតាមការចង់បាន"},
                {icon: "fa-calendar-check", step: "3", title: "ការប្រតិបត្តិ", cnTitle: "完美执行", desc: "រៀបចំកម្មវិធីយ៉ាងល្អឥតខ្ចោះនៅថ្ងៃពិសេស"}
            ].map(item => (
                <div class="text-center bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition relative group">
                    <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-primary text-white text-3xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-white shadow-md relative z-10 group-hover:bg-gold transition">
                        <i class={`fas ${item.icon}`}></i>
                        <span class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border-2 border-white">{item.step}</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1 font-heading">{item.title}</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2 font-chinese">{item.cnTitle}</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
            ))}
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="gallery" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-dark font-heading mb-2">ស្នាដៃចុងភៅម្ហូបការរបស់យើង</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 font-chinese">我们的宴会作品展示</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="columns-1 md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-4 space-y-4">
        {gallery.map((img, index) => (
            <div class="break-inside-avoid rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer bg-gray-100 relative">
                <img 
                    src={img} 
                    alt={`CKM Food ${index}`} 
                    class="w-full h-auto object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" 
                    loading="lazy" 
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-300"></div>
            </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')] opacity-20"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-heading">ទាក់ទងមកយើងខ្ញុំ</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl text-white/90 font-chinese mb-6">立即联系我们，打造完美盛宴</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-red-100 mb-10">
        កម្មវិធីដ៏ល្អឥតខ្ចោះមួយ ចាប់ផ្តើមពីការពិភាក្សាដ៏សាមញ្ញ។
        <br/>
        <span class="text-sm font-chinese opacity-80">一场完美的活动，始于一次简单的沟通。</span>
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12">
        {phoneNumbers.map((contact) => (
            <a href={`tel:+855${contact.num.replace(/\s/g, '').substring(1)}`} class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary text-white border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group">
                <i class={`fas ${contact.icon} text-3xl mb-2 text-gold group-hover:text-primary`}></i>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold font-heading">{contact.num}</span>
                <span class="text-xs opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 uppercase tracking-widest">{contact.type}</span>
            </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
        <a href={facebookLink} target="_blank" class="w-14 h-14 bg-white text-[#1877F2] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl hover:scale-110 transition shadow-lg">
          <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
        </a>
        <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" class="w-14 h-14 bg-white text-[#229ED9] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl hover:scale-110 transition shadow-lg">
          <i class="fab fa-telegram-plane"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-[#1e2732] py-10 border-t border-gray-700 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <img src={logo} class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border border-gray-600 opacity-80">
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-md">
            <p class="mb-1">ផ្ទះលេខ 33 ផ្លូវ 257 សង្កាត់ទឹកល្អក់ទី២ ខណ្ឌទួលគោក រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ</p>
            <p class="font-chinese opacity-80">地址：金边市堆谷区第257路33号</p>
          </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
        &copy; 2026 CKM Catering Service. All Rights Reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
